  "Description": "Find managers with at least five direct reports",
  "sql": "SELECT name FROM Employee WHERE id IN (SELECT managerId FROM Employee GROUP BY managerId HAVING COUNT(id) >= 5);",
  "Explanation": "This SQL query first groups the employees by their managerId and counts the number of direct reports for each manager. It then selects the names of managers whose direct reports count is equal to or greater than 5."
